<Algorithm code="           1. Let _taRecord_ be MakeTypedArrayWithBufferWitnessRecord(_O_, ~seq-cst~).           1. Let _keys_ be a new empty List.           1. If IsTypedArrayOutOfBounds(_taRecord_) is *false*, then             1. Let _length_ be TypedArrayLength(_taRecord_).             1. For each integer _i_ such that 0 ≤ _i_ &lt; _length_, in ascending order, do               1. Append ! ToString(𝔽(_i_)) to _keys_.           1. For each own property key _P_ of _O_ such that _P_ is a String and _P_ is not an integer index, in ascending chronological order of property creation, do             1. Append _P_ to _keys_.           1. For each own property key _P_ of _O_ such that _P_ is a Symbol, in ascending chronological order of property creation, do             1. Append _P_ to _keys_.           1. Return _keys_.         ">
